#: ../../library/omv.image.rst:318
msgid ""
"Grayscale histograms have one channel with some number of bins. All bins "
"are normalized so that all bins sum to 1."
msgstr "灰度直方图有一个通道，一些数目的柱。所有柱都被归一化，以便所有柱的和等于 1。"

#: ../../library/omv.image.rst:321
msgid ""
"RGB565 histograms have three channels with some number of bins each. All "
