"currently as it has a GPU that can do this in hardware."
msgstr "``transform`` 是一个 3x3 的 ``ndarray``，用于对图像执行透视变换。目前仅在 OpenMV Cam N6 上支持，因为它有可以在硬件中完成此操作的 GPU。"

#: ../../library/omv.image.rst:1854 ../../library/omv.image.rst:1931
#: ../../library/omv.image.rst:1995 ../../library/omv.image.rst:2059
#: ../../library/omv.image.rst:2123 ../../library/omv.image.rst:2187
#: ../../library/omv.image.rst:2251 ../../library/omv.image.rst:2315
