#: ../../library/omv.image.rst:2516 ../../library/omv.image.rst:2653
#: ../../library/omv.image.rst:2717
msgid ""
"``copy`` if True create a deep-copy on the heap of the image that's been "
"converted versus converting the original image in-place."
msgstr "``copy`` 如果为 True，则在堆上创建图像的深拷贝，而不是就地转换原始图像。"

#: ../../library/omv.image.rst:1857 ../../library/omv.image.rst:1934
#: ../../library/omv.image.rst:1998 ../../library/omv.image.rst:2062
#: ../../library/omv.image.rst:2126 ../../library/omv.image.rst:2190
